address.streetAddress: The 1594 with 3 car garage Plan, Stone's Throw

location.fullValue: The 1594 with 3 car garage Plan, Stone's Throw

data.description: This well maintained home lives large thanks to its optimized functional floor plan. On the light-filled main level you will find the kitchen with ample storage and oversized pantry that flows into a dedicated dining room with access to the expansive deck and views of the backyard. New LVP flooring on the main level! There are two bedrooms on the main level including a SECOND primary suite with a private bathroom! The double sided staircase allows access to the upstairs from the kitchen and front entryway. Upstairs features three oversized bedrooms with opportunity for your personal charm. Second and third bedroom upstairs have a Jack and Jill bath! The backyard has a partially covered patio, garden space, is fully fenced, and has a cozy gazebo with an outdoor fireplace. Newer roof, two separate AC units for each floor, furnace, and hot water heater. Great schools and community with access to shopping, freeways, and all you need. Large attached garage also has a huge storage area. Very unique property that is difficult to find!
